Editor (and sometimes whole workbench) messes up when playing with the double slash in:
```scala
package test

object Comment {
  //def f = 0 
}
```

Sometimes it appears right after typing the slashes, sometimes after deleting one. The error log spawns lots of errors, e.g.:
